                                                                   --Project Instructions--
                                                                   

There are two endpoins
----------------------
 
 -Load the currency exchange rate into database
      Hit URL on POST method
      
      1) http://localhost:8081/currency-converter/{can-be-any-date}
        
        -Example :- http://localhost:8081/currency-converter/2021-04-01
         
         -There are validation on date
           a) Allow date till past 12 months 
           b) Allow 1st day of month date only 
           c) Not allow future date
 
 
 
 -Fetch currency exchage rates data in Json format as a result
       Hit URL on GET method
       
      1)Example :-  http://localhost:8081/currency-converter/daterange?from=2020-10-11&to=2021-08-11
      
